sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Admin
    participant B as Browser
    participant W as WebThaoCamVien (AdminController)
    participant DB as WebContext (SQL Server)

    U->>B: Mo /Admin/Monitoring
    B->>W: GET /Admin/Monitoring

    Note over W: AuthN/AuthZ (cookie)

    par Lay so lieu tong hop
        W->>DB: Query health status (Web/API/DB)
        DB-->>W: healthSummary
    and Lay thong ke loi/latency
        W->>DB: Query request logs + exception logs (rolling window)
        DB-->>W: errorRate + latencySeries
    and Lay tinh trang dong bo
        W->>DB: Query sync backlog / retry queue (neu co)
        DB-->>W: syncBacklog
    end

    W-->>B: 200 View(MonitoringViewModel)
    B-->>U: Render tiles + charts + danh sach su co gan day

    opt Dieu tra su co
        U->>B: Bam drill-down (filter endpoint/status/POI)
        B->>W: GET /Admin/Monitoring?from&to&filter...
        W->>DB: Query chi tiet (paging)
        DB-->>W: rows
        W-->>B: 200 Partial/JSON (tuy thiet ke)
        B-->>U: Cap nhat bang/chi tiet
    end
